      "name": "Hemolysis index comparison across 5 flow-speed operating points",
      "description": "CFD-predicted normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) compared against in-vitro measurements at 5 operating points. RH < 1 criterion satisfied at all points. No uncertainty quantification provided for predicted or experimental values."
    },
